name: FamilyMeals
0:
”Alexa, open Family Meals”
”Ask Family Meals to give me a meal idea”
”Ask Family Meals to give me a suggestion”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: family meals
des: Are you trying to decide what to make for dinner? Maybe you're trying to plan out a week's worth of meals for your family. This skill will provide a random suggestion for a meal. If you want more suggestions, just use the skill repeatedly.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
